## Prose slides

# Authored in `.work`

Speaker notes live in the slide header. Body text supports **emphasis**, lists, and `inline code` — rendered with deck typography before the stage loads.



preload do
  /reactable/labs/chart.html?deck=showcase
  /reactable/labs/whiteboard.html?deck=demo
  https://tldraw.com
end



script do
  id: open
  on: deck.open
  run: echo 'showcase deck — media formats tour'
  detach: true
end



slide do
  id: start
  type: client
  notes: Title slide — designed client island
  unit: showcase_title
end

slide do
  id: format-prose
  type: prose
  notes: Prose slides use theme title / section / closing
  theme: section
end

slide do
  id: format-iframe-local
  type: iframe
  notes: Same-origin lab — full bleed in stage frame
  url: /reactable/labs/chart.html?deck=showcase
  title: Local iframe app
  action: wait 500
end

slide do
  id: format-client
  type: client
  notes: Client islands — full custom HTML
  unit: pulse_slide
end

slide do
  id: format-iframe-remote
  type: iframe
  notes: Cross-origin embed when network allows
  url: https://tldraw.com
  title: Remote iframe
  action: wait 1500
end

slide do
  id: format-video
  type: video
  notes: Native HTML5 video — local MP4 from decks/showcase/labs/
  src: /reactable/labs/sample.mp4?deck=showcase
  action: play
end

slide do
  id: format-youtube
  type: youtube
  notes: Big Buck Bunny on YouTube — embed-friendly; some videos block embedding
  videoId: aqz-KE-bpKQ
  action: wait 800
end

slide do
  id: format-whiteboard
  type: iframe
  notes: Interactive canvas lab
  url: /reactable/labs/whiteboard.html?deck=demo
  title: Whiteboard lab
  action: wait 300
end

slide do
  id: end
  type: prose
  notes: Closing slide
  theme: closing
end
